Dad’s know it all! From life tricks to fashion trends! 

So here’s to my dear papa! @minusonelifestyle the style that compliments his stature ❤️

Do you still miss Kk’s voice?🥹💔
what music! what movie! Once in a lifetime 🤌🏻😭 @kk_live_now @ipritamofficial 

That era of Kk was so different ! Bollywood in that period gave us so many magical songs ! composition by Pritam or the soulful voice of KK that touches all the high notes and makes you feel every single word of the song to its depth !!!

Now that kk is not with us, the only way to keep his legacy alive is his music, so here is my tribute to one of the most musically gifted Bollywood song by our very own dear Kk Sir!

My parents used to tell me in my childhood how great Lata Ji and Kishor da were. I will be telling my kids about KK and surely my kids will be his fan after listening to his legendary voice. 🛐❤️
